<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
1.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Banana plug
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Put tire (2) to which air bag (inflator) module is secured on tire (1) without wheel and place 2 tires (3) with wheel on them and place tire (4) with wheel on top.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Harness of special tool (A) and special tool (B) should not be too tight under tire. Otherwise, harness may be pulled to cause breakage when air bag deploys.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Secure tires with cord (5).
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820093.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "70.661mm" ver = "01" gw = "176" gh = "184"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
