<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
6.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Banana plug
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<topic id = "AENCP70A8206026004">
<title>
Deployment
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Stretch deployment harness (A) to its full length 10 m (33 ft), and then place 12 V vehicle battery (1) near shorted end of deployment harness (A).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B096">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B097">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-76510">
09932–76510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Separate two banana plugs (2) on deployment harness.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Notify all people in immediate area that you intend to deploy air bag (inflator) module or activate seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness to 12 V vehicle battery.
</ptxt>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not place deployed air bag (inflator) module and activated seat belt pretensioner near any flammable objects.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not apply water, oil, etc. to deployed air bag (inflator) module and activated seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Wait for about 30 minutes before touching any metal surface of air bag (inflator) module or seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
<figure page = "1">
<graphic graphicname = "IAW10A820047.swf" width = "183.000mm" height = "173.642mm" ver = "01" gw = "473" gh = "476"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1" page = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.757in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "1.492in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.394in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.918in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Blanket
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Clear space 185 cm (6 ft)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“a”.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
10 m (33 ft)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Put on safety glasses (1) and pair of shop gloves (2) to protect your eyes and hands from possible irritation and heat when handling deployed air bag (inflator) module or activated seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Dispose of deployed air bag (inflator) module or activated seat belt pretensioner through normal refuse channels after it has cooled for at least 30 minutes and tightly seal air bag (inflator) module or seat belt pretensioner in strong vinyl bag.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I8T201821025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "61.136mm" ver = "01" gw = "162" gh = "157"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Wash your hands with mild soap and water afterward.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</topic>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A8206026005">
<title>
Deployment / Activation Inside of Vehicle
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Place vehicle on safe place and fully close all windows.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Completely cover windshield area and front door window opening with drop cloth, a blanket or any similar item (1). This reduces possibility of injury due to possible fragmentation of vehicle’s glass or interior.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820094.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.772mm" ver = "01" gw = "154" gh = "119"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Disable air bag system. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A8206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect special tool according to part to be activated.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Driver Air Bag (Inflator) Module
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove steering column lower cover. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A6206001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Disconnect contact coil assembly connector (2) as follows.
</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Release locking slider (1) by sliding it in direction of arrow “1”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Disconnect contact coil assembly connector (2) by pulling it in direction of arrow “2”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness (A) and adapter cable (B) to contact coil side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B098">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B099">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-77310">
09932–77310
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820106.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "69.041mm" ver = "01" gw = "235" gh = "179"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Passenger Air Bag (Inflator) Module
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove glove box. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9306001"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Disconnect passenger air bag (inflator) module connector (2) as follows.
</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Release locking slider (1) by sliding it in direction of arrow “1”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Disconnect passenger air bag (inflator) module connector (2) by pulling it in direction of arrow “2”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness (A) and adapter cable (B) at passenger air bag (inflator) module side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0100">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0101">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-78332">
09932–78332
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820096.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "68.332mm" ver = "01" gw = "236" gh = "177"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Seat Belt Pretensioner
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove center pillar lower trim. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Disconnect pretensioner connector (2) from retractor pretensioner as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Release lock (1).
</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Disconnect connector (2) with lock released.
</ptxt>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness (A) and adapter cable (B) to retractor pretensioner.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0102">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0103">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-76510">
09932–76510
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820097.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "74.545mm" ver = "02" gw = "228" gh = "195"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Side-Air Bag (Inflator) Module
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Disconnect side-air bag (inflator) module connector (2) as follows.
</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Release locking slider (1) by sliding it in direction of arrow “1”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Disconnect side-air bag (inflator) module connector (2) by pulling it in direction of arrow “2”.
</ptxt>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness (A) and adapter cable (B) to connector at side-air bag (inflator) module side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0104">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0105">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-78332">
09932–78332
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820098.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.805mm" ver = "01" gw = "223" gh = "108"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<ptxt>
<emph>
Curtain Air Bag (Inflator) Module
</emph>
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Remove front pillar trim, center pillar upper trim / lower trim and rear pillar inner trim. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A9806009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Disconnect curtain air bag (inflator) module connector (2) from curtain air bag (inflator) module as shown in figure.
</ptxt>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Release lock (1).
</ptxt>
</s3>
<s3>
<ptxt>
Disconnect connector (2) with lock released.
</ptxt>
</s3>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Connect deployment harness (A) and adapter cable (B) to connector at curtain air bag (inflator) module side.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0106">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0107">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-78332">
09932–78332
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820099.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "89.689mm" ver = "01" gw = "229" gh = "238"/>
</figure>
</s2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check that there is no person inside vehicle or in close area. Remove any object that can be flown off or flammable object due to deployed air bag (inflator) module or activated seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Place 12 volts vehicle battery (1) near shorted end of deployment harness.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L8B0108">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09932-75031">
09932–75031
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I9P60A820100.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "51.428mm" ver = "02" gw = "206" gh = "129"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "6" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.266in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.705in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.266in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.922in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.842in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
2.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Blanket
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
3.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Banana plug
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" align = "right">
<ptxt>
4.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
10 m (33 ft)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Separate banana plug of deployment harness.
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Notify all people in immediate area that you intend to deploy air bag (inflator) module or activate seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Connect banana plug of deployment harness to battery.
</ptxt>
<attention1>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not place deployed air bag (inflator) module and activated seat belt pretensioner near any flammable objects.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Do not apply water, oil, etc. to deployed air bag (inflator) module and activated seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Wait for about 30 minutes before touching any metal surface of air bag (inflator) module or seat belt pretensioner.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention1>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
</servinfo>
